{"word":"μυστιλάομαι","slug":"μυστιλάομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μυστιλάομαι</b></el> <el>(μυστῑλάομαι,) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to sop bread in soup</i> or <i>gravy and eat it</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>: <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>μυστιλᾶται τῶν δημοσίων</el> <i>he ladles out</i> public money, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> sense, <i>scooped out</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>μυστί¯λη</el>\n"}]}